# Postmortem: search outage
## Summary
Search was down 25min.
## Timeline (UTC+8)
- 14:30 down  - 14:55 up
## Impact
60% users, 25 min.
## Root cause (5-Why)
The Elasticsearch node was OOM-killed. Root cause: memory limit too low. We fixed it by
raising the limit. That's the root cause: the limit was too low.
## Resolution
Raised memory limit to 8Gi.
## Lessons learned
Memory limits matter.
## Action items
- @sre raise limit (done), due 2026-06-01
